info.name: /trunblock
info.description: Unblock a user or role from your channel.
examples: /trunblock @sheiks - The role `sheiks` will be unblocked from your channel.
/trunblock 669975205325570048 @naju - The role of ID `669975205325570048` and the user `naju` will be unblocked from your channel.
/trunblock 919664522267070534 862740130385494027 286166598048284683 @naju - All these members will be unblocked from your channel.
